@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<article>
    <h4>Introduction:</h4>
    <p>
        This GDPR policy page outlines how we, [Company Name], collect, process, and store your personal data in accordance with the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
    </p>
    <h4>Personal Data We Collect:</h4>
    <p>
        We collect personal data such as your name, email address, phone number, address, and other contact details when you interact with our website, products, or services. We may also collect other data such as your IP address, browsing history, and location data when you use our website.
    </p>
    <h4>How We Use Your Personal Data:</h4>
    <p>
        We use your personal data to provide you with our products or services, to communicate with you, to improve our website and services, and for other legitimate business purposes. We may also use your data for marketing purposes with your explicit consent.
    </p>
    <h4>Data Sharing and Transfers:</h4>
    <p>
        We may share your personal data with our service providers and partners who help us to deliver our products and services to you. We may also transfer your data to third-party countries outside the EU, but we will ensure that appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data.
    </p>
    <h4>Your Rights:</h4>
    <p>
        You have the right to access, modify, and delete your personal data, as well as the right to restrict or object to our processing of your data. You also have the right to withdraw your consent for marketing communications at any time.
    </p>
    <h4>Data Security:</h4>
    <p>
        We take appropriate measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, use, and disclosure. We also regularly review our security practices and update our systems to ensure they meet the latest security standards.
    </p>
    <h4>Contact Us:</h4>
    <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about our GDPR policy or your personal data, please contact us at [contact email]. We will do our best to address your concerns and resolve any issues in a timely manner.
    </p>
    <h4> Updates to Our Policy:</h4>
    <p>
        We may update this GDPR policy page from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will post the updated policy on our website and notify you of any significant changes.
    </p>
</article>
